text: Azangulovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Novomeshcherovsky Selsoviet, Mechetlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 326 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 29 km from Bolsheustyikinskoye, 6 km from Novomeshcherovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mechetlinsky District
title: Azangulovo
